be handed over to south korea soon 
the un command which polices panmunjom consists of 
representatives of the united states and 15 other countries that 
helped south korea drive out invading north koreans in the 195053 
korean war 
china fought with north korea and signed the 1953 ceasefire 
todays defection is the first known chinese defection through 
panmunjom north koreans russians and czechoslovakians have 
defected there 
