have obtained refuge in the country in june a state department 
spokesman said other chinese officials have asked washington for 
protection but he refused to elaborate 
fang and ms li fled to the us embassy after chinese troops 
marched on unarmed protesters in beijing and killed hundreds 
perhaps thousands china says only 100 civilians and nearly 100 
soldiers and police died 
