year brought in 140 hunters and an estimated 100000 of new 
spending 
one hundred thousand dollars is an attentiongetter in this 
town said billy don atkinson a robybased federal agriculture 
official who helps run the coop 
and in fisher county theyll try anything 
the commission is hoping to build a memorial garden for slain 
